# Installation

# Summary
This package contains type definitions for geokdbush (https://github.com/mourner/geokdbush).

# Details
Files were exported from https://github.com/DefinitelyTyped/DefinitelyTyped/tree/master/types/geokdbush.
## [index.d.ts](https://github.com/DefinitelyTyped/DefinitelyTyped/tree/master/types/geokdbush/index.d.ts)
````ts
import { KDBush } from "kdbush";

export function around<T>(
    index: KDBush<T>,
    longitude: number,
    latitude: number,
    maxResults?: number,
    maxDistance?: number,
    filterFn?: any,
): T[];

export function distance(
    longitude1: number,
    latitude1: number,
    longitude2: number,
    latitude2: number,
): number;

````
